    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and minor scuffs on the bumpers, though there is no major structural damage. Inside, the upholstery shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat, and while the AC and radio work perfectly, the rear power windows are currently non-functional. Mechanically, it starts up every time and drives fine, but it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid, functional car that just needs a little TLC to be brought back to its best.",
