    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. Everything runs smoothly, the interior is comfy, and it's totally ready for its next adventure! Come take it for a spin, I think you're really going to love how it handles.",
