    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering 320 hp through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. It has been proactively maintained with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The cooling system is optimized with a low-temp thermostat and high-flow water pump. The chassis remains sharp, featuring refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a driver-focused example ready for the circuit or canyon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
