    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been meticulously cared for. The exterior finish maintains a beautiful gloss, with only the minor road chips and light swirls expected from a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the interior is clean and inviting; the seats are firm and supportive, showing only light natural creasing in the leather, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital display works perfectly, ensuring a seamless driving experience. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The brakes are responsive, and the suspension provides a comfortable, composed ride. With plenty of life left in the tires and a clean title in hand, this car is ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable service and pride of ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
